maintext:
ROCKY HILL, Conn. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the Connecticut Lottery’s “Lucky Links Night” game were:
02-04-05-06-09-12-16-21
(two, four, five, six, nine, twelve, sixteen, twenty-one)
